{
  "texts": [
    "Studies that are not directly related to the integration of machine learning in AML practices are also excluded.",
    "Additionally, publications older than 5 years are excluded to prioritize recent advancements and insights.",
    "Papers not written in English are excluded as they may pose challenges for understanding and analysis.",
    "The inclusion and exclusion criteria are summarized in Table 3.1.",
    "Fifty-two (52) papers were included in this study based on the various inclusion and exclusion criteria."
  ]
